A man received a thorough beating at the Likoni ferry for allegedly ejaculating on a woman.The unidentified woman said she detected an "abnormally slippery" feeling on her behind and upon checking, found that the man had started ejaculating on her.Angry commuters attacked the man who was later taken away by security officials while unconscious.The incident took place at 6.30pm on Thursday just as the ferry, MV Kilindini, was midway across the Likoni channel. It was bound for Mombasa mainland.The suspect was taken to the Mainland's police station.Women have complained about instances of sexual harassment on the Likoni channel.